{"word":"H2600 - חִנָּם - chinnâm - khin-nawm' - Without a cause","slug":"H2600","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חִנָּם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>chinnâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khin-nawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Without a cause"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05DD; - chinna&#x0302;m</b> - <i>khin-nawm'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2580\">H2580</a>; <i>gratis</i>, that is, devoid of cost, reason or advantage: - without a cause (cost, wages), causeless, to cost nothing, free (-ly), innocent, for nothing (nought), in vain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2433\">H2433</a>, <a href=\"#/H2580\">H2580</a>, <a href=\"#/H2581\">H2581</a>, <a href=\"#/H2582\">H2582</a>, <a href=\"#/H2584\">H2584</a>, <a href=\"#/H2586\">H2586</a>, <a href=\"#/H2587\">H2587</a>, <a href=\"#/H2589\">H2589</a>, <a href=\"#/H2592\">H2592</a>, <a href=\"#/H2594\">H2594</a>, <a href=\"#/H2603\">H2603</a>, <a href=\"#/H2605\">H2605</a>, <a href=\"#/H2606\">H2606</a>, <a href=\"#/H2607\">H2607</a>, <a href=\"#/H2608\">H2608</a>, <a href=\"#/H2615\">H2615</a>, <a href=\"#/H8467\">H8467</a>, <a href=\"#/H8468\">H8468</a>, <a href=\"#/H8469\">H8469</a>"}]}